* to initiate and maintain high-level contact with interested parties, both local and international, in relevant areas of the operations of the Agency;
* to monitor and supervise the preparation of the annual budgets and reports of the Agency for the review and approval of the Board;
* to overseethe work and discipline of the other staff of the Agency;
* to carry out such other functions as may be assigned by the Board or necessary for the purposes of the Agency; and
* serve as Secretary to the Board.
